title: Typical Weekday Year 2009 PeMS Flows and Speeds
name: Typical Weekday Year 2009 PeMS Flows and Speeds
description:
Metropolitan Transportation Commission
Summary of Caltrans Perfomance Measurement System (PeMS) data.
http://pems.dot.ca.gov/
Includes data from March, April, May, September, October, and November 2009.
Includes data for Tuesdays, Wednesdays, and Thursdays.
Largely excludes imputed data.
Excludes data present only for part-, rather than full-days.
Intended to represent typical day flows and speeds.
Flows aggregated to MTC travel model time periods (http://mtcgis.mtc.ca.gov/foswiki/Main/TimePeriods).
Offsets introduced to coordinates to distinguish bi-directional count stations.
